      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，LR从左到右。节点标签就用Infra_前缀加组件名，比如Infra_EtcdCluster这样，统一风格。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "flowchart LR",
        "Infra_EtcdCluster",
        "Infra_LoadBalancer",
        "Infra_IngressController",
        "Infra_RedisCache"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把四个节点放上去，从左到右排列。第一个是Infra_EtcdCluster，然后是Infra_LoadBalancer、Infra_IngressController，最后是Infra_RedisCache。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_EtcdCluster",
        "Infra_LoadBalancer",
